Implement functionalities to retrieve and update the compute fleet status.

The value stored in the table is a json in the following form
{
    "status": "STOPPING",
    "lastStatusUpdatedTime": "2021-12-21 18:12:07.485674+00:00",
}

Parse s3 url to get bucket name and object name.

input: s3://test/templates/3.0/post_install.sh
output: {"bucket_name": "test", "object_key": "templates/3.0/post_install.sh", "object_name": "post_install.sh"}

Return Security groups by nodes.

The result is a set of frozenset,
e.g. {frozenset(security groups for head node), frozenset(security groups for queue 1), ...}

